// Datasheet for the `cache` device: it also requires storage for a `Node` shape, minimum 16 rows.
// This is the SAME shared shape the `store` device uses — devices share shapes by structure. A driver
// importing both must provide ONE pool that meets the max of the two minimums. Support file.
// RUN: true
Node :: arche { key :: float, val :: float }
Node[16]
